{"tid":1133854,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"一人n個打鬥遊戲中設計得太強大嘅角色","createTime":"2019-05-01T11:24:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-01T15:45:32.000Z","uid":108894,"like":3,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0131ac099952a3df5ecc69d4f2b761af985333b3","tid":1133854,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T11:24:26.000Z","msg":"其中之一一定係Brawl Stars新出嘅Rosa<br />\n<br />\n最初必殺技可以持續6秒減傷80%<br />\n最恐怖係儲氣快，更過份有必殺時攻擊可以繼續再儲氣，者係只要不停擊中對方，必殺可以不斷開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而且如果玩踢波最過份係佢開左必殺可以帶波，而且冇技術含量，就咁大搖大擺帶波入龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (如果對面冇Frank嘅話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n就算而家nerf到持續4秒減傷70%依然都係太變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (因為帶必殺攻擊時不影響儲氣嘅設定冇變<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n想睇Nita/El Primo單挑Rosa，應該都會死得非常慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦因為Rosa新出咁幾乎全世界都買黎用 (包括我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因為19石就有，實在抵到唔識講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"f98a9d26a5f4349c386a023060d8866e97117ebf","tid":1133854,"uid":199162,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"邪鬼"},{"pid":"26a8bc72ab60cc044410d4ed8e02d389d138c947","tid":1133854,"uid":227000,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T11:37:40.000Z","msg":"其實沖杯真係好難 自問自己都唔廢 但係永遠出去玩啲隊友永遠係10lv英 但係操作同1lv英無分別 每次都係輸隊友<br />\n利申470杯crow"},{"pid":"dee3f8c5880f7b5cbbf22813deb62b570becc4ad","tid":1133854,"uid":48759,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T11:38:14.000Z","msg":"原來bs係打鬥遊戲"},{"pid":"a47ad206a6ba4d7370b6d7215611b9f55f259ab1","tid":1133854,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"f98a9d26a5f4349c386a023060d8866e97117ebf","tid":1133854,"uid":199162,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"邪鬼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T11:38:22.000Z","msg":"回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係邪鬼有樣野好，就係要破解至有，隻Rosa最cls連佢係Brawl Stars竟然係Rare級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (Brawl Stars稀有度Legendary&gt;Mythic&gt;Super Rare&gt;Rare&gt;Starting<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，根本係一隻合法外掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e340a6024c7317d81adae3c3c9a4d224c36e3a6c","tid":1133854,"uid":15823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dee3f8c5880f7b5cbbf22813deb62b570becc4ad","tid":1133854,"uid":48759,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T11:38:14.000Z","msg":"原來b